    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Let Them Come: Onslaught》中迎接无情的外星人袭击——这是一款弹幕天堂式的Roguelike射击游戏，充满了复古科幻经典的粗犷气息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从夸张的武器库和爆炸性的升级中打造完美构筑，在复古混乱的火海中歼灭外星部落。若你渴望一场80年代风格的科幻动作生存体验，并配以Cartridge 87创作的震撼节奏原声，这款游戏绝不会让你失望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种武器解锁</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/aeaa05906508a749ad9562bb234e63e3.poster.avif?t=1771532182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/aeaa05906508a749ad9562bb234e63e3.webm?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/aeaa05906508a749ad9562bb234e63e3.mp4?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用一整套科幻电影般的武器释放你内心的动作英雄——从喷火器到光子军刀，应有尽有。你甚至可以从轨道上发射核弹——确保彻底清除敌人。每种武器都有独特的玩法，升级还能叠加毁灭性连招。无论你偏爱群体清场火力、精准打击，还是拯救性的护盾，都可定制你的装备，实现极致杀伤（与极致风格）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深度可重玩性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/952b60dfbc4f28df53ada67b18528fe6.poster.avif?t=1771532182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/952b60dfbc4f28df53ada67b18528fe6.webm?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/952b60dfbc4f28df53ada67b18528fe6.mp4?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次游玩都独一无二。战斗间隙中，构建你的技能组合，投入辛苦赚取的资源来解锁与强化新能力，优化策略并深入敌方领地。尝试是关键——实验不同武器的协同效果，融合特殊能力，直到你的无敌构筑只留下外星废墟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>波次生存战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/126ac25aa24e381bc64a295756fd61a5.poster.avif?t=1771532182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/126ac25aa24e381bc64a295756fd61a5.webm?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/126ac25aa24e381bc64a295756fd61a5.mp4?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着外星攻势愈发猛烈，你的反应与战术将受到极限考验。若能幸存足够久，将面对庞大的首领，需要全力以赴。这是来自复古科幻动作黄金时代的终极对决。整装待发，开火迎敌——Onslaught即将开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗跨越世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/a040310fba8b3227e49033c58dde9a4b.poster.avif?t=1771532182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/a040310fba8b3227e49033c58dde9a4b.webm?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2050800/extras/a040310fba8b3227e49033c58dde9a4b.mp4?t=1771532182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在四个截然不同的环境中奋战。地图不断变化，动态事件层出不穷：意外出现的迷你首领、远处的补给投放，以及可选目标的随机任务，都将考验你的临场应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏的 弹幕天堂 式战斗</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度 roguelite 养成与构筑系统</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>程序生成地图与动态事件</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cartridge 87 原创合成波配乐</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两位可操控角色：士兵与灵能者</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 个独特世界与史诗级首领战</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在 Onslaught 中生存多久？</p>",
